             was indicted for <rs id="t17831210-98-off510" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831210-98-off510" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831210-98-off510" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17831210-98-cd511" type="crimeDate">5th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-98-off510 t17831210-98-cd511"></join> last, one cloth great coat, value 3 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-98-victim1057" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Wellings
                        <interp inst="t17831210-98-victim1057" type="surname" value="Wellings"></interp>
